Comparison with AV1/HEVC/VVC
| Codec        | Compression    | Complexity             |
| ------------ | -------------- | ---------------------- |
| AVC          | Moderate       | Low                    |
| HEVC         | High           | High                   |
| AV1          | Very High      | Very High              |
| VVC          | Extremely High | Extremely High         |
| LCEVC + AVC  | Improved       | Moderate               |
| LCEVC + HEVC | Very High      | Lower than native HEVC |


